summary.span: 將多個值的雜湊碼合併成單一雜湊碼。

span.span: Combines the hash code for multiple values into a single hash code.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您可以使用結合成單一雜湊程式碼的多個值 （例如，結構或類別上的欄位）。You can use to combine multiple values (for example, fields on a structure or class) into a single hash code. 此結構的操作中有兩種：This structure operates in one of two ways: * 接受一組結合最多八個值的靜態方法。Static methods that accept a set of up to eight values to combine. * 兩個執行個體運作中資料流處理的方式，一次接受一個值的方法。Two instance methods that operate in a streaming fashion, accepting values one at a time. > [!WARNING] > 因為實作可能會在組件版本之間變更，就視為實作詳細資料的雜湊碼的最佳做法。It is best-practice to consider hash codes as an implementation detail, as the implementation may change across assembly versions. 不會儲存所產生的雜湊碼中序列化的結構，例如，在磁碟上。Do not store hash codes produced by in serialized structures, for example, on-disk. 您可以使用以靜態方式初始化的隨機種子，強制執行此最佳做法，這表示雜湊程式碼只具決定性的作業系統處理序的範圍內。 uses a statically initialized random seed to enforce this best practice, meaning that the hash codes are only deterministic within the scope of an operating system process. ### 靜態方法Static Methods 靜態方法結合最多八個值的預設雜湊程式碼。The static methods combine the default hash codes of up to eight values. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#1](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example1.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example1.vb#1)] ### 執行個體方法Instance Methods > [!IMPORTANT] > 必須呼叫每個執行個體的最多一次。 must be called at most once per instance of . 執行個體方法結合超過八個值的雜湊碼。The instance methods combine the hash codes of more than eight values. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#2](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example2.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#2](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example2.vb#1)] 執行個體方法也會結合特定所產生的雜湊碼實作。The instance methods also combine the hash codes produced by a specific implementation. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#3](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example3.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#3](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example3.vb#1)] 結構必須傳遞藉由參考於其他方法，因為它是實值型別。The structure must be passed by-reference to other methods, as it is a value type. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#4](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example4.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#4](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example4.vb#1)]
